<plot>Pedro Armendariz incarnate for the first time in his career the revolutionary warrior Pancho Villa. During the Mexican Revolution, Martin Corona (Rodolfo Acosta) wants to marry with his girlfriend, but the arrival of the federal army to his small town stop this romantic purpose. Later, Pancho Villa (Armendáriz) arrives with his army to the town and takes the power. Corona, searched by the federal army, joins Villa's army but he will have to choose between his duty as a soldier and the love of his girlfriend.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?644463</url></doc>
